  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety and effectiveness of the ROX Coupler used to create an arteriovenous
      anastomosis in the iliac region (between the iliac artery and vein) in subjects with
      hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
